    <briefdescription>
<para>This file contains the implementation of LMS client interface functions. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It packages an IPI request that asks the server-side LMS handler (XSecure_LmsSignVerifyIpi -&gt; XSecure_LmsSignatureVerification) to verify an LMS signature against a message and an expected public key.</para><para><preformatted>
